  An integral component in design is language. Defined literally, language is a method of communication, which may be spoken or written. Language is the essence behind visualising your product idea. Sketching is a form of language that is used to communicate initial ideas.

  One of the first steps in the development of your product idea is to visualise and convey your idea by sketching. We encourage team members to upload and share concept sketches for brainstorming.

